sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant BE as Backend<br/>Express API
    participant N8N as N8N<br/>Workflow Engine
    participant Groq as Groq AI<br/>LLM Service
    participant DB as Database<br/>PostgreSQL
    participant DC as Discord<br/>Bot Service

    Note over BE, DC: Workflow 1 - Ticket Intelligence (AI Classify + Summary)

    BE ->> N8N: POST /webhook/discord-activity<br/>(event=ticket.created, ticketId)
    activate N8N
    N8N ->> BE: GET /api/ticket/:id
    activate BE
    BE ->> DB: ticket.findUnique (id)
    activate DB
    DB -->> BE: ticketData
    deactivate DB
    BE -->> N8N: ticketData
    deactivate BE

    N8N ->> Groq: Prompt - classify type,<br/>priority, category
    activate Groq
    Groq -->> N8N: type, priority, category, suspect_area
    deactivate Groq

    N8N ->> Groq: Prompt - generate summary tiket
    activate Groq
    Groq -->> N8N: summary text
    deactivate Groq

    N8N ->> Groq: Prompt - smart recommendation
    activate Groq
    Groq -->> N8N: recommendation array
    deactivate Groq

    N8N ->> BE: POST /api/ticket/summary<br/>(ticketId, summary, recommendations)
    activate BE
    BE ->> DB: ticket.update (summary, keywords)
    activate DB
    DB -->> BE: updated
    deactivate DB
    BE -->> N8N: success
    deactivate BE

    N8N ->> DC: Update thread dengan summary AI
    activate DC
    DC -->> N8N: message sent
    deactivate DC
    deactivate N8N

    Note over BE, DC: Workflow 2 - Chatbot Assistant

    BE ->> N8N: POST /webhook/chatbot-qa<br/>(question, userId, context)
    activate N8N
    N8N ->> BE: GET /api/knowledge
    activate BE
    BE ->> DB: knowledgeBase.findMany()
    activate DB
    DB -->> BE: entries array
    deactivate DB
    BE -->> N8N: context data
    deactivate BE
    N8N ->> Groq: Prompt - jawab dengan context KB
    activate Groq
    Groq -->> N8N: answer text
    deactivate Groq
    N8N ->> BE: POST /api/chatbot/log
    activate BE
    BE ->> DB: chatbotInteraction.create (log)
    deactivate BE
    N8N ->> DC: Kirim jawaban ke Discord thread
    activate DC
    DC -->> N8N: sent
    deactivate DC
    deactivate N8N

    Note over BE, DC: Workflow 3 - Incident Handler + Smart Intake

    BE ->> N8N: POST /webhook/incident-event<br/>(event=incident.created, ticketId)
    activate N8N
    N8N ->> BE: GET /api/ticket/:id
    activate BE
    BE -->> N8N: incidentData
    deactivate BE
    N8N ->> Groq: Prompt - analisis root cause,<br/>mitigasi, dan dampak incident
    activate Groq
    Groq -->> N8N: root_cause, mitigation_steps, impact
    deactivate Groq
    N8N ->> BE: POST /api/ticket/timeline/append
    activate BE
    BE ->> DB: ticket.update (root_cause, timeline)
    activate DB
    DB -->> BE: updated
    deactivate DB
    BE -->> N8N: success
    deactivate BE
    N8N ->> DC: Post analisis ke thread Discord
    activate DC
    DC -->> N8N: posted
    deactivate DC
    deactivate N8N